snippet.title: ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS - CHARACTER TRAILER #4
snippet.description:
The Hero Association has sent back up! 3 new heroes are joining the ranks in ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS!  

ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS! arrives February 28th, 2020! Pre-order your copy today! https://bandainam.co/OnePunchManPO
